{"tid":166763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個on9老母事跡","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T11:20:09.000Z","uid":81817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8093868d532df9276b83ed82621b78efd01a290c","tid":166763,"uid":81817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"我老母個好朋友嫁女<br />\n叫我同佢一齊去飲<br />\n去到我老母擺底封人情就立刻搵佢朋友吹水啦<br />\n本來無嘜野，點知我老母突然好大聲咁問：<br />\n恭喜你就快做人阿嫲啦，你個女個肚幾個月大啦？<br />\n嚇到我即刻拉走我老母<br />\n我老母仲唔知錯話我咁老土，呢啲好事黎<br />\n但係人地唔只係大肚結婚，仲要拍咗兩個月就結婚<br />\n仲仲仲要個女結婚當日未夠18歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390bdea1ed6569186de89148ea4bd500776c1a34","tid":166763,"uid":53694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b44cf2377d05be40a5f3f5eb79ab444e267c4c","tid":166763,"uid":12882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8a837e7834fa992979fe4a055e6e0dcfe77876","tid":166763,"uid":68410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"生咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc9510625805ee8d2c7155d63dd41a665c4230e","tid":166763,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo